                </h1>
                
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-10">
                    In New Zealand, if you don't answer, they call the next bloke on Google. <br/><br/>
                    Deploy a <strong>SystemPros AI Receptionist</strong> today: It answers instantly 24/7, speaks with a natural <strong>Kiwi accent</strong>, and books jobs directly into your calendar while you sleep (or fish).
                </p>
                
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
                    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 border-blue-500 text-white shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(37,99,235,0.4)]">
                        Deploy AI in NZ
                    </a>
                    <a href="#calculator" class="btn btn-secondary border-white/20 hover:bg-white/5">
                        Calculate Lost Revenue
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- The Problem: The Silent Killer -->
    <section id="comparison" class="py-24 bg-gray-950 border-t border-white/5 relative">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="text-center mb-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">The <span class="text-red-500">Silent Killer</span> of NZ Service Businesses</h2>
                <p class="text-secondary text-lg">You spend thousands on Google Ads to make the phone ring. Why are you letting 40% of those calls go to voicemail?</p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
                <!-- Traditional Way -->
                <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-red-500/30 transition-all">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-red-500"></div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
                        <span class="p-2 bg-red-500/10 rounded-lg text-red-500"><X /></span>
                        The "Human" Bottleneck
                    </h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-6">
                        <li class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-2">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                <Coins className="w-5 h-5 text-red-400" />
                                <span class="text-secondary">Wage Cost</span>
                            </div>
                            <span class="font-mono text-red-400 font-bold">$65k+ / year</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-2">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                <PhoneMissed className="w-5 h-5 text-red-400" />
                                <span class="text-secondary">Missed Calls</span>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-white">High (Lunch, Busy, Sick)</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-2">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                <Clock className="w-5 h-5 text-red-400" />
